data.description: Better than new home perfect for your family.  9 foot ceilings and E insulated glass windows with screens, LPV flooring, recessed lighting and a 50 gallon electric water heater and granite counter tops are only a few of the amazing features of this 3 bedroom 2 bath home.  With the Guarded Gate of this water front community, you can enjoy the community dock, boat ramp, two pools, tennis courts, playgrounds and much more.  You are 15 minutes away from the Historic Granbury Square where you can enjoy fabulous dining, shopping and entertainment.
